paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the regulation of KCNH2 gene expression by PABPN1, focusing on alternative polyadenylation and its effects on Kv11.1 isoform expression. No specific genetic variants in KCNH2 were reported.

challenges: The paper did not report specific genetic variants in KCNH2.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the regulation of KCNH2 gene expression and did not provide specific genetic variant data.
